+ Response 422 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + request_id: `a1c7f92d-5f1b-4f09-9e3d-1e2f7e8b2c11` (string, required) - Request ID
        + success: false (boolean, required) - Request success flag
        + timestamp: `2025-01-15T10:05:23.412Z` (string, required) - Request timestamp
        + error (object, required) - Error information
            + code: `VALIDATION_ERROR` (string, required) - Code
            + message: `Validation failed` (string, required) - Message
            + details (array, optional) - Validation errors
                + (object)
                    + field: `email` (string, required) - Field name
                    + message: `Invalid email format` (string, required) - Error message
                + (object)
                    + field: `name` (string, required) - Field name  
                    + message: `Name is required` (string, required) - Error message

+ Response 429 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + request_id: `a1c7f92d-5f1b-4f09-9e3d-1e2f7e8b2c11` (string, required) - Request ID
        + success: false (boolean, required) - Request success flag
        + timestamp: `2025-01-15T10:05:23.412Z` (string, required) - Request timestamp
        + error (object, required) - Error information
            + code: `RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED_ERROR` (string, required) - Code
            + message: `Too many requests` (string, required) - Message
            + details (object, optional) - Rate limit details
                + retry_after: 60 (number, required) - Seconds to wait before retry
                + limit: 1000 (number, required) - Rate limit threshold
                + remaining: 0 (number, required) - Remaining requests
                + reset: `2025-01-15T10:06:23.412Z` (string, required) - Reset timestamp

